summary:
"Alone we can do so little; together we can do so much." 

I strongly believe that when we make an effort to understand the other, we can thrive of each otherâ€™s strengths â€“ making for a better world. I am passionate about bringing People & Opportunities together and believe in embracing the role of technology as an accelerator for progress and to face the challenges of today.

My drive and energy I get from meeting and working across borders, with people & organisations wanting to progress and collaborate on ideas with the aim to generate impact. It is this drive and endless resilience what attracts me in particular to emerging markets â€“ where highly skilled talent is ready to create a better future. 

I hold a solid understanding of varying market contexts and a global network that connects both mature and developing markets. Always happy to engage, connect and collaborate.
